                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/05/237301566/bf4346b2af8799209a3a494f359067a7_8906688900072372819.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Народ Родников",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Tupac grew up in the People of the Springs.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7490,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Теноч",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Tenoch was Tupac's greatest foe of youth. The giant left him 200 minor wounds, 2 broken ribs, and one eye that will never again perceive distance. When Tenoch became the leader of the tribal coalition forces during the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7089,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/12/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_1090730713764694732.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Катаклизм в Каэнри'ах",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", Tupac was the last to join him.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7472,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Хаборим",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Tupac agreed with the Pyro Archon's plan and fought alongside her against the Abyss. He was the one who carried Mavuika to the Sacred Flame so she could enter it and be reborn in 500 years.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 6319,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/08/26/f4c75caad42923eb91ee760aa2eb473a_7439123622315070718.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Mualani",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "One of the six heroes of Natlan who participated in Haborym's plan and the heir of the Ancient Name Umoja.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
